{"tid":679893,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本8日7夜點plan好？","createTime":"2018-05-26T21:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T03:55:15.000Z","uid":45332,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a08bf25ed10cf538a210ba5e8f677f486bca2fab","tid":679893,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T21:51:50.000Z","msg":"Day 0<br />\n夜晚十一點機東京羽田行<br />\n<br />\n宿：飛機<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 <br />\n清晨4：55落機，<br />\n搭頭班車出築地，<br />\n之後秋葉原9行，<br />\n3點去住宿check in,<br />\n再去新宿/秋葉原9行<br />\n<br />\n宿：東京<br />\n<br />\nDay 2<br />\n一早出東京站換JR pass, <br />\n買立山黑部加購票(9000yen)<br />\n上大宮鐵博，<br />\n落江之島<br />\n返新宿9行<br />\n<br />\n宿：東京<br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n一早新幹線上輕井澤9行<br />\n睇下有冇時間去松本城9行<br />\n<br />\n宿：長野站附近酒店<br />\n<br />\nDay 4<br />\n一早用立山黑部加購票<br />\n係長野東口搭高速巴士去扇澤上立山，<br />\n預計6點前落返富山站，<br />\n去金澤近江町搵野食？<br />\n<br />\n宿：金澤東口某酒店<br />\n<br />\nDay 5<br />\n一早搭雷鳥落京都，<br />\n去嵐山小火車？即場買票會唔會死？<br />\n去京都鐵博<br />\n落返大阪<br />\n<br />\n宿：大阪<br />\n<br />\nDay 6<br />\n未諗<br />\n<br />\n宿：大阪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 7<br />\n未諗<br />\n<br />\n宿：大阪<br />\n<br />\nDay 8<br />\n未諗<br />\n夜晚8點機關西走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴絲比啲意見，獨遊第一次plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0658189239f66bb81c6079792a1b2c14e1f193e7","tid":679893,"uid":90706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T22:00:04.000Z","msg":"幾時去？"},{"pid":"987045a876fd40b0e64dd2ad2bd00f832ff170a0","tid":679893,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0658189239f66bb81c6079792a1b2c14e1f193e7","tid":679893,"uid":90706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T22:00:04.000Z","msg":"幾時去？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T22:06:07.000Z","msg":"下月頭"},{"pid":"e9a7532270ad6bbded7c7ba4d29bb01e2385a22d","tid":679893,"uid":145839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T22:20:40.000Z","msg":"第一次日本？"},{"pid":"b8315fd83b221653b497fa247b1e3c65cb6ff6a2","tid":